1
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:34,520
=Lady Liberty=

2
00:01:35,020 --> 00:01:37,940
=Episode 36=

3
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:41,120
First of all,

4
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:43,640
I've gathered the requests
from this group of students.

5
00:01:43,880 --> 00:01:45,120
They hope to increase

6
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,440
the proportion of AI co-writing.

7
00:01:46,880 --> 00:01:48,760
They believe
it's the trend of the future.

8
00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:50,280
I can't do that.

9
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,640
I'm teaching people how to write novels,

10
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:54,240
not how to use AI.

11
00:01:55,644 --> 00:01:57,520
Besides, I don't even
know how to use it myself.

12
00:01:57,533 --> 00:01:58,555
How can I teach it?

13
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:00,600
Second,

14
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:02,800
Dai Shan wants you
to visit Lingqi Platform.

15
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,320
Not going.

16
00:02:05,720 --> 00:02:06,880
Third,

17
00:02:07,022 --> 00:02:08,933
Zhangzhu has also signed with Dai Shan.

18
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:09,920
What?

19
00:02:11,120 --> 00:02:11,920
Mr. He Han,

20
00:02:12,920 --> 00:02:14,720
don't worry
about hurting my self-esteem.

21
00:02:15,120 --> 00:02:16,360
Just tell it like it is.

22
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:20,120
Am I any good at writing novels?

23
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,040
You're okay.

24
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,680
But I'm not the particularly
talented type, right?

25
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,800
It's fine. Just tell me the truth.

26
00:02:29,400 --> 00:02:30,040
I...

27
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:31,760
can't become you,

28
00:02:31,920 --> 00:02:33,920
can't become Lin Zhanqiao,

29
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,320
and I can't

30
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:36,640
even become

31
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:38,555
someone like Gu Yan
or Hong Qigong, right?

32
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,640
No, you can't say that.

33
00:02:41,720 --> 00:02:43,044
- Everyone...
- Anyway, I'm just

34
00:02:43,200 --> 00:02:45,200
not the gifted type, right?

35
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:49,520
No.

36
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,880
You're right. I know it myself.

37
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,840
But I still want to be

38
00:03:01,080 --> 00:03:02,080
someone a bit different.

39
00:03:03,920 --> 00:03:05,120
I want you

40
00:03:06,200 --> 00:03:07,640
to look at me in a new light

41
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,760
for just a moment.

42
00:03:11,311 --> 00:03:12,622
Wait, what does that have to do

43
00:03:12,640 --> 00:03:14,000
with you going to Lingqi Platform?

44
00:03:15,288 --> 00:03:16,840
I'm going as an undercover agent.

45
00:03:18,044 --> 00:03:19,160
If I go, won't I find out

46
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:20,440
what they're actually up to?

47
00:03:20,711 --> 00:03:22,466
We will know whether
they're truly capable

48
00:03:22,533 --> 00:03:23,377
or just all talk.

49
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,480
Who asked you to go?

50
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,560
No one asked me to go.

51
00:03:27,640 --> 00:03:28,960
I decided to go on my own.

52
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:30,360
Then, who do you plan to share

53
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,840
the information you gather with?

54
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:32,840
A lot of people.

55
00:03:32,960 --> 00:03:34,288
For example, Prefrontal Cortex,

56
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,800
Mustard Salad, Zhugan Dalang,

57
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,480
and some you don't know,

58
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:40,177
the writers from our
Brain-on-Paper Team.

59
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:42,160
- What team?
- Let me analyze your zodiac sign.

60
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:44,720
- We've formed a "Brain-on-Paper" team.
- I don't follow.

61
00:03:44,911 --> 00:03:45,880
It's just a team of

62
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:48,000
young writers who
weren't recruited by Dai Shan.

63
00:03:48,320 --> 00:03:50,480
There are new writers from Chenxing

64
00:03:50,560 --> 00:03:52,480
and some writers
from your training class.

65
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:53,977
Let me state this clearly.

66
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:55,560
It's not that we're rejecting AI.

67
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,920
We're rejecting
having our aesthetics and tastes

68
00:03:57,920 --> 00:03:59,280
tightly controlled by AI big data.

69
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:03,360
And we're talking about
daily updates from everyone.

70
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:05,600
A serious daily check-in
of at least 5,000 words.

71
00:04:08,760 --> 00:04:09,880
This team of yours...

72
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:11,200
It is still growing.

73
00:04:12,760 --> 00:04:14,360
Mimi has been a huge help.

74
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:16,000
She's the one who gave me

75
00:04:16,010 --> 00:04:17,120
your students' contact info.

76
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,680
Hello! Good work, everyone.

77
00:04:18,680 --> 00:04:20,600
I bought some food and drinks
to fuel your brains.

78
00:04:20,600 --> 00:04:21,800
- Thanks.
- Much appreciated.

79
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:23,120
- Thanks for the milk.
- Thank you, Mimi.

80
00:04:23,120 --> 00:04:23,940
- There's enough for everyone.
- Take a look at

81
00:04:23,940 --> 00:04:25,180
- our detailed outline for this chapter.
- Okay.

82
00:04:27,222 --> 00:04:28,720
Does your boss know about this?

83
00:04:31,080 --> 00:04:31,560
No.

84
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:35,520
But I think I still need to tell her.

85
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:36,320
Because...

86
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:39,520
I want to ask her to let us
use the Chenxing office.

87
00:04:39,777 --> 00:04:40,880
The lease for that place

88
00:04:40,880 --> 00:04:42,120
hasn't expired yet, right?

89
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:43,400
Besides,

90
00:04:43,640 --> 00:04:44,800
every meeting we had before

91
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,680
was at my place.

92
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:48,280
But now that I'm an undercover agent,

93
00:04:48,377 --> 00:04:49,844
we can't keep meeting at my house.

94
00:04:49,880 --> 00:04:52,022
It would be too easy
to blow my cover, right?

95
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:55,640
Not bad, Cai Zhangzhu.

96
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,200
I already see you in a new light.

97
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,920
You've grown quite capable now.

98
00:04:59,280 --> 00:05:00,480
The fate of the industry

99
00:05:01,511 --> 00:05:02,977
is every woman's responsibility.

100
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,160
Thanks.

101
00:05:09,266 --> 00:05:10,177
Enjoy your meal.

102
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:20,360
I have two paths before me now.

103
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:22,240
First,

104
00:05:22,488 --> 00:05:23,600
I go to Hong Kong, China.

105
00:05:24,200 --> 00:05:25,600
In a few years, I'll be successful,

106
00:05:25,800 --> 00:05:27,155
and then I'll return home in glory.

107
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:28,520
The other one,

108
00:05:29,800 --> 00:05:30,400
I stay.

109
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:34,200
But I'll lose all
my clients and connections.

110
00:05:34,560 --> 00:05:35,400
I'll lose Catherine.

111
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,400
I'll have to start over as a nobody.

112
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:41,680
But I can keep pursuing you.

113
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,560
Even if the odds are against me.

114
00:05:49,311 --> 00:05:51,080
Only a fool would
choose the second path.

115
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,480
So you made the right choice.

116
00:05:54,320 --> 00:05:55,560
Maybe I'm just that fool.

117
00:05:56,555 --> 00:05:57,666
What do you mean?

118
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,640
I've already chosen the second path.

119
00:06:01,888 --> 00:06:03,800
Aren't you going
to Hong Kong, China, tomorrow?

120
00:06:05,444 --> 00:06:06,320
Before coming here,

121
00:06:06,320 --> 00:06:08,733
I already told Catherine
I'm not going to Hong Kong, China.

122
00:06:08,866 --> 00:06:10,040
Even though I still hoped

123
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,840
to hear you ask me to stay,

124
00:06:12,644 --> 00:06:13,680
I've made this decision,

125
00:06:13,777 --> 00:06:14,680
and it won't change.

126
00:06:17,440 --> 00:06:18,160
Are you serious?

127
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:32,120
I don't want this decision

128
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:34,840
to affect your future.

129
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:37,720
It won't.

130
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:41,560
I'm the one who chose to pursue love.

131
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,080
I might lose some opportunities,

132
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:46,280
but I'll earn back
what I've lost myself.

133
00:06:46,720 --> 00:06:47,440
If I can't,

134
00:06:47,888 --> 00:06:49,080
then I'm simply not worthy.

135
00:06:53,200 --> 00:06:54,360
Of course, years from now,

136
00:06:54,360 --> 00:06:56,320
if you see a down-and-out me,

137
00:06:56,355 --> 00:06:58,533
I hope you won't look
down on me too much.

138
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:00,320
Just give me some time.

139
00:07:00,440 --> 00:07:01,040
That's all.

140
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:03,280
I won't look down on you.

141
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,720
When you first saw me at the hospital,

142
00:07:05,720 --> 00:07:06,844
you were quite dismissive.

143
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:08,400
I was dismissive then,

144
00:07:08,555 --> 00:07:09,770
but I won't be in the future.

145
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,520
Dinner is on me today.

146
00:07:40,480 --> 00:07:41,920
I was thinking of coming to see you

147
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:43,190
since you were leaving tomorrow.

148
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,600
But you got here first.

149
00:07:45,960 --> 00:07:48,240
I happened to have some things
I needed your help with,

150
00:07:48,880 --> 00:07:50,400
so I came by to see you.

151
00:07:51,044 --> 00:07:52,640
I've already made plans with your dad.

152
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:54,560
I'll go play chess with him every week.

153
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:56,320
I know. He told me.

154
00:07:57,440 --> 00:07:59,720
So, he even went out
and bought a new chessboard.

155
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:01,640
Don't worry.

156
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,560
There's one more thing.

157
00:08:06,680 --> 00:08:07,080
Go on.

158
00:08:08,960 --> 00:08:11,400
The lease for Chenxing's office
still has a month left.

159
00:08:11,920 --> 00:08:14,240
So I've left it to Zhangzhu
and her Brain-on-Paper Team.

160
00:08:16,022 --> 00:08:17,680
It doesn't feel like
I've been away long,

161
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:19,840
but it seems like
a lot of time has passed.

162
00:08:21,333 --> 00:08:23,355
I've already spoken to
the property management.

163
00:08:23,377 --> 00:08:25,170
The cleaning lady
is coming this afternoon.

164
00:08:25,180 --> 00:08:27,440
After that, you all can come
and use the place anytime.

165
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:28,440
Thanks, Ms. Lin.

166
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,440
This is great.

167
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:31,488
I feel like we're part of
the regular army now.

168
00:08:32,560 --> 00:08:33,240
Good luck to you.

169
00:08:34,880 --> 00:08:35,600
In the future,

170
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:37,520
if they need any help

171
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,040
and you happen to be free,

172
00:08:39,688 --> 00:08:40,888
please give them a hand.

173
00:08:42,244 --> 00:08:43,520
They're a bunch of young people,

174
00:08:44,280 --> 00:08:45,320
just like we used to be.

175
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:46,800
Full of passion.

176
00:08:48,560 --> 00:08:49,080
No problem.

177
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,880
These are some outlines and directions

178
00:08:59,880 --> 00:09:02,040
I wanted to work on,
but never got around to.

179
00:09:02,377 --> 00:09:03,480
They're quite suitable

180
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:05,520
as entry-level choices
for the current market.

181
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,520
I think they might be

182
00:09:07,644 --> 00:09:09,111
useful for Zhangzhu and her team.

183
00:09:09,311 --> 00:09:11,333
At least it can help
broaden their thinking.

184
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:12,840
Got it.

185
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:15,720
And about Gu Yan...

186
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,560
If they continue to
challenge Phantom Knight

187
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:20,280
or spread malicious rumors,

188
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:22,120
I've already consulted Ma.

189
00:09:22,533 --> 00:09:24,088
We can gather evidence and sue.

190
00:09:25,022 --> 00:09:26,111
What do you think?

191
00:09:26,440 --> 00:09:27,280
He's not worth it.

192
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:28,120
Agreed.

193
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,711
What time is your flight tomorrow?

194
00:10:06,822 --> 00:10:08,377
Let me drive you to the airport.

195
00:10:13,200 --> 00:10:13,760
No need.

196
00:10:19,644 --> 00:10:21,244
Then, take care of yourself.

197
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:27,680
Don't worry.

198
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:42,120
I'm off then.

199
00:12:29,800 --> 00:12:30,720
Did you call a car?

200
00:12:33,120 --> 00:12:33,720
Yes, I did.

201
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,240
It should be here soon.

202
00:12:39,866 --> 00:12:41,000
Let me walk you to the car.

203
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:41,720
No need.

204
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:54,040
This is far enough.

205
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:02,440
Okay.

206
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:13,960
Lin Zhanqiao.

207
00:13:49,380 --> 00:13:53,300
(Year 2015)

208
00:13:53,444 --> 00:13:54,520
(Heaven's Fall by Phantom Knight)
Lin Zhanqiao, look!

209
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:55,440
He Han!

210
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:57,120
He Han!

211
00:13:57,880 --> 00:13:59,080
He Han!

212
00:14:00,640 --> 00:14:01,600
He Han, look.

213
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,520
Happy birthday!

214
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:05,880
Happy birthday,

215
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:08,840
(Heaven's Fall by Phantom Knight)
Phantom Knight!

216
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:31,300
(Phantom Knight Design Studio)

217
00:15:27,222 --> 00:15:28,680
If you had come ten minutes earlier,

218
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:30,400
He Han would still be here.

219
00:15:32,280 --> 00:15:33,280
Today, he broke his rule

220
00:15:34,280 --> 00:15:35,760
