a connection.

232
00:16:47,520 --> 00:16:47,960
Thanks.

233
00:17:40,580 --> 00:17:42,100
(Zhanqiao: Mei, I'm leaving tomorrow.
Let's skip the goodbyes)

234
00:17:42,100 --> 00:17:43,420
(to avoid the sadness.
I'll call you when I arrive.)

235
00:17:50,260 --> 00:17:55,020
(May: Worlds apart, yet close at heart.
Safe travels.)

236
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:12,800
♪I keep asking myself♪

237
00:18:14,600 --> 00:18:17,930
♪What it is I should become♪

238
00:18:19,560 --> 00:18:29,130
♪To follow what my heart truly wants♪

239
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:40,230
♪Like a drifting dandelion♪

240
00:18:42,100 --> 00:18:45,280
♪Turning where it drifts♪

241
00:18:46,020 --> 00:18:51,170
♪Into soil where it can grow♪

242
00:18:52,950 --> 00:18:56,290
♪When the rain comes, I hide♪

243
00:18:56,730 --> 00:18:59,640
♪In a flower shop at the corner♪

244
00:19:00,450 --> 00:19:05,820
♪Even spring borrows its fragrance♪

245
00:19:07,710 --> 00:19:14,140
♪Moonlight keeps me company
on lonely roads♪

246
00:19:14,870 --> 00:19:21,040
♪Across fields of blooms,
a boat awaits me♪

247
00:19:22,040 --> 00:19:28,880
♪Swaying in the shape of the wind♪

248
