255
00:19:44,022 --> 00:19:45,120
Here, this is for you two.

256
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:46,200
Mr. He Han.

257
00:19:46,600 --> 00:19:47,840
Mr. He Han, you're here.

258
00:19:47,880 --> 00:19:49,840
- Welcome, Mr. He Han.
- Hello, Mr. He Han.

259
00:19:50,080 --> 00:19:51,080
So lively here.

260
00:19:51,800 --> 00:19:52,760
Of course.

261
00:19:52,760 --> 00:19:53,910
Keep it up, Brain-on-Paper Team.

262
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:55,760
- The legend is here.
- Welcome, Mr. He Han.

263
00:19:55,880 --> 00:19:57,444
- I invited Mr. He Han
- Welcome, Mr. He Han.

264
00:19:57,466 --> 00:19:58,280
to be your consultant.

265
00:19:58,280 --> 00:19:59,240
Good, please.

266
00:19:59,400 --> 00:19:59,880
Mr. He Han,

267
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:01,000
look, what we have here

268
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:02,880
are our existing works

269
00:20:02,880 --> 00:20:04,040
and recent backlogs.

270
00:20:04,360 --> 00:20:05,280
Not bad.

271
00:20:05,840 --> 00:20:07,120
If you have any questions,

272
00:20:07,120 --> 00:20:08,040
feel free to ask me.

273
00:20:08,480 --> 00:20:10,000
Besides, Lin Zhanqiao asked me to come,

274
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:11,440
so you should thank her.

275
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:14,688
These are some high-potential
outlines she left for everyone.

276
00:20:14,733 --> 00:20:16,800
If you want to start
a new work but lack inspiration,

277
00:20:16,800 --> 00:20:18,420
you can refer to these anytime. Alright?

278
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:20,360
Thank you so much, Mr. He Han.

279
00:20:20,760 --> 00:20:22,800
You can use Ms. Lin's old office.

280
00:20:22,840 --> 00:20:23,440
Is that okay?

281
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:24,440
That's perfect.

282
00:20:24,560 --> 00:20:26,990
Good. Ms. Lin left something for you.
I'll go get it for you.

283
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:27,320
Sure.

284
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:31,520
Li, come down and take a look.

285
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:49,360
Mr. He Han,

286
00:20:49,440 --> 00:20:49,760
here.

287
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:52,000
I'll head out now.

288
00:20:52,080 --> 00:20:52,400
Okay.

