00:22:56,800 --> 00:22:57,200
Mr. Fan.

297
00:22:58,420 --> 00:23:00,580
("The Yin-Dragon Decree")

298
00:23:05,240 --> 00:23:06,000
Hello, Mr. Fan.

299
00:23:07,600 --> 00:23:08,711
Hello, Mr. Fan.

300
00:23:16,760 --> 00:23:17,160
Mr. Fan.

301
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:20,400
We received a novel from Phantom Knight.

302
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,577
I've put it on your desk.

303
00:23:21,680 --> 00:23:22,080
Who?

304
00:23:22,400 --> 00:23:23,200
Phantom Knight.

305
00:23:24,840 --> 00:23:26,800
Still joking at a time like this?

306
00:24:09,680 --> 00:24:10,080
Hello?

307
00:24:10,320 --> 00:24:10,760
Hello.

308
00:24:11,640 --> 00:24:13,360
I'm from Dingqi. My last name is Fan.

309
00:24:14,800 --> 00:24:16,560
I just received

310
00:24:16,920 --> 00:24:18,920
a novel signed by Phantom Knight titled

311
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:20,560
"My Life Envies No Immortal."

312
00:24:21,640 --> 00:24:22,520
You sent this, right?

313
00:24:23,160 --> 00:24:24,240
Excuse me, who is this?

314
00:24:25,200 --> 00:24:26,400
It's me, Mr. Fan.

315
00:24:26,520 --> 00:24:27,160
He Han.

316
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:31,600
Why are you making this kind of joke?

317
00:24:32,480 --> 00:24:34,520
I wouldn't choose
a time like this to joke around.

318
00:24:36,560 --> 00:24:37,320
Do you know

319
00:24:37,622 --> 00:24:39,520
how many people I have
to deal with every month

320
00:24:39,640 --> 00:24:41,480
who claim to be Phantom Knight?

321
00:24:43,000 --> 00:24:44,000
If you don't believe me,

322
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:45,600
you can call Ma yourself.

323
00:24:46,000 --> 00:24:47,440
He's Phantom Knight's editor.

324
00:24:47,440 --> 00:24:48,400
He can prove it.

325
00:24:50,511 --> 00:24:51,555
Have some tea.

326
00:24:56,560 --> 00:24:57,080
So,

327
00:24:58,080 --> 00:24:59,720
Zhanqiao isn't Phantom Knight.

328
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:03,040
Since you are Phantom Knight,

329
00:25:03,040 --> 00:25:04,680
why did you suddenly stop writing

330
00:25:04,777 --> 00:25:06,466
and switch back to your real name?

331
00:25:07,720 --> 00:25:08,680
Personal reasons.

332
00:25:09,680 --> 00:25:10,400
So that time,

333
00:25:11,120 --> 00:25:12,480
your "Shattered Six States"

334
00:25:12,680 --> 00:25:15,320
plagiarized Phantom Knight's
"Parting with Yan Dan at Yishui."

335
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:17,840
Essentially, you were copying yourself.

336
00:25:18,520 --> 00:25:19,360
Is that why you

337
00:25:20,400 --> 00:25:22,360
didn't come forward to clarify things?

338
00:25:22,520 --> 00:25:24,177
How could I? Under those circumstances,

339
00:25:24,222 --> 00:25:25,720
if I had explained everything,

340
00:25:25,720 --> 00:25:27,022
wouldn't I have exposed myself?

341
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:29,680
Then, what about now?

342
00:25:30,222 --> 00:25:31,488
Are you no longer afraid?

343
00:25:31,888 --> 00:25:33,920
Instead, you've come out
to reveal your identity.

344
00:25:40,400 --> 00:25:40,960
Right now,

345
00:25:42,160 --> 00:25:43,800
at the old Chenxing office,

346
00:25:44,080 --> 00:25:45,600
there are over a dozen young authors

347
00:25:45,600 --> 00:25:47,177
who are persisting with their novels.

348
00:25:48,360 --> 00:25:50,880
They are full of passion and
want to challenge Lingqi Platform.

349
00:25:51,488 --> 00:25:53,720
But their influence is limited
if they're on their own.

350
00:25:55,720 --> 00:25:57,480
If Phantom Knight takes the lead,

351
00:25:58,440 --> 00:25:59,200
this confrontation

352
00:26:00,222 --> 00:26:01,520
might actually be worth a shot.

353
00:26:12,600 --> 00:26:14,680
Even if I believe what you've said,

354
00:26:15,160 --> 00:26:16,440
on what basis should I believe

355
00:26:17,400 --> 00:26:18,800
that you can still produce

356
00:26:19,080 --> 00:26:21,600
work of the same
high standard as before?

357
00:26:22,680 --> 00:26:23,600
Zhanqiao is gone.

358
00:26:23,600 --> 00:26:25,360
You don't even have a decent editor.

359
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:30,680
Because you have no choice.

360
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:32,400
You have to believe me.

361
00:26:45,920 --> 00:26:48,640
(Phantom Knight's stunning comeback,
real identity shocks the internet.)

362
00:26:48,640 --> 00:26:50,900
(A new work created by
He Han and Lin Zhanqiao.)

363
00:26:54,340 --> 00:26:56,940
(Phantom Knight returns.
Dingqi invites you to a literary feast.)

364
00:27:07,380 --> 00:27:10,500
(Phantom Knight returns.
Dingqi invites you to a literary feast.)

365
00:27:16,900 --> 00:27:19,420
(Phantom Knight)

366
00:27:29,600 --> 00:27:30,280
Fan,

367
00:27:31,120 --> 00:27:31,960
where did you

368
00:27:31,960 --> 00:27:34,040
find another Phantom Knight from?

369
00:27:34,840 --> 00:27:36,000
No comment.

370
00:27:57,888 --> 00:27:58,800
Did you ask Mr. Fan?

371
00:27:58,800 --> 00:27:59,644
What did he say?

372
00:28:00,088 --> 00:28:01,822
I couldn't get anything out of him.

373
00:28:02,560 --> 00:28:03,680
What do you mean by that?

374
00:28:04,880 --> 00:28:05,920
It means

375
00:28:06,488 --> 00:28:08,000
I don't know what he's up to either.

376
00:28:09,360 --> 00:28:10,880
Usually when I ask him things,

377
00:28:11,520 --> 00:28:13,440
he'll give me a mix of truth and lies.

378
00:28:13,466 --> 00:28:15,040
But this time, no matter what I ask,

379
00:28:15,040 --> 00:28:16,000
he has no reaction.

380
00:28:16,200 --> 00:28:17,240
He's not hiding anything,

381
00:28:17,400 --> 00:28:18,800
but he's not bragging either.

382
00:28:19,240 --> 00:28:20,120
What does that mean?

383
00:28:22,760 --> 00:28:23,840
Don't you know him well?

384
00:28:24,520 --> 00:28:26,200
Has the real Phantom Knight returned?

385
00:28:26,400 --> 00:28:28,720
Didn't you also suspect
that Lin Zhanqiao was Phantom Knight?

386
00:28:28,720 --> 00:28:29,600
But she's already gone abroad.

387
00:28:29,600 --> 00:28:30,640
What's really going on here?

388
00:28:31,800 --> 00:28:34,320
Even if Lin Zhanqiao
isn't Phantom Knight,

389
00:28:34,320 --> 00:28:35,920
the author who Fan has

390
00:28:36,800 --> 00:28:38,960
can't possibly be
the real Phantom Knight either.

391
00:28:44,133 --> 00:28:45,444
Who could it be, then?

392
00:28:46,680 --> 00:28:48,600
The title of the new novel
has been released,

393
00:28:49,480 --> 00:28:50,840
which means there's content.

394
00:28:51,577 --> 00:28:53,266
If the content wasn't good enough,

395
00:28:53,333 --> 00:28:55,222
Mr. Fan wouldn't
dare to launch it so rashly.

396
00:29:00,360 --> 00:29:01,040
This shows that,

397
00:29:02,320 --> 00:29:03,520
to some extent,

398
00:29:04,480 --> 00:29:05,600
he is very confident.

399
00:29:08,840 --> 00:29:09,920
It's also possible

400
00:29:09,955 --> 00:29:11,911
he's just making a last-ditch effort.

401
00:29:14,800 --> 00:29:16,040
I don't care what the reason is.

402
00:29:16,511 --> 00:29:18,040
I want you to tell me
as quickly as possible

403
00:29:18,040 --> 00:29:19,360
who this Phantom Knight really is.

404
00:29:20,240 --> 00:29:20,640
Also,

405
00:29:21,040 --> 00:29:22,000
no matter who he is,

406
00:29:22,640 --> 00:29:24,160
after the novel goes online,

407
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:27,240
none of his data can exceed mine.

408
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:30,800
Don't worry.

409
00:29:31,840 --> 00:29:33,200
This project is nothing more than

410
00:29:33,200 --> 00:29:35,760
using the Phantom Knight name
as a gimmick.

411
00:29:36,120 --> 00:29:37,560
It just has a bit better traffic.

412
00:29:37,560 --> 00:29:39,320
It won't be a good project.

413
00:29:39,760 --> 00:29:40,960
If it were a good project,

414
00:29:40,960 --> 00:29:42,480
Fan would have brought it out long ago.

415
00:29:42,480 --> 00:29:44,111
He wouldn't have waited until now.

416
00:29:55,066 --> 00:29:56,600
Why are you looking at me like that?

417
00:29:58,560 --> 00:29:59,760
Are you getting nervous?

418
00:30:01,160 --> 00:30:01,960
Me, nervous?

419
00:30:02,688 --> 00:30:04,533
I see you've been
drinking water constantly.

420
00:30:17,160 --> 00:30:18,200
When did this happen?

421
00:30:18,800 --> 00:30:19,200
It...

422
00:30:19,733 --> 00:30:21,000
It's been so many years that he...

423
00:30:21,840 --> 00:30:23,720
I entered this industry because of him.

424
00:30:28,760 --> 00:30:29,640
Hello, Mr. He Han.

425
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:31,040
Did you see the news?

426
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:34,000
Phantom Knight is going
to serialize a new novel.

427
00:30:34,480 --> 00:30:36,120
It's the real Phantom Knight himself.

428
00:30:36,640 --> 00:30:37,200
I saw it.

429
00:30:37,422 --> 00:30:38,440
Let's wait and see.

430
00:30:51,620 --> 00:30:54,940
(Chapter 52: Luoshui Overflows,
No Fish in Sight)

431
00:30:55,360 --> 00:30:57,160
(Phantom Knight's latest work)
Now is the time

432
00:30:57,640 --> 00:30:59,880
for each of us
to bring out our best resources

433
00:31:00,040 --> 00:31:00,960
and give it our all.

434
00:31:01,600 --> 00:31:03,160
We'll see who has the real skill.

435
00:31:04,240 --> 00:31:04,880
No problem.

436
00:31:06,560 --> 00:31:08,400
So, who exactly is Phantom Knight?

437
00:31:11,111 --> 00:31:12,044
He's here.

438
00:31:20,040 --> 00:31:20,800
He Han?

439
00:31:21,360 --> 00:31:21,960
It's He Han.

440
00:31:22,800 --> 00:31:25,120
He Han has been frequenting
Dingqi Platform lately,

441
00:31:25,360 --> 00:31:26,880
having closed-door meetings with Fan.

442
00:31:27,440 --> 00:31:28,040
I checked.

443
00:31:28,560 --> 00:31:31,000
He has stopped all his
online and offline classes.

444
00:31:31,920 --> 00:31:33,520
The writer behind Phantom Knight

445
00:31:33,520 --> 00:31:34,600
must be He Han.

446
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:36,640
That's why Fan

447
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:38,440
dared to say the work wouldn't be bad.

448
00:31:40,520 --> 00:31:41,600
Why is it him again?

449
00:31:46,920 --> 00:31:47,720
Mr. He Han,

450
00:31:48,520 --> 00:31:49,720
Dai Shan found out it's you.

451
00:31:51,640 --> 00:31:52,320
What did she say?

452
00:31:52,577 --> 00:31:54,880
As soon as she returned to the company,
she told everyone

453
00:31:55,040 --> 00:31:56,911
that the person behind
Phantom Knight's return

454
00:31:56,955 --> 00:31:57,866
is you, Mr. He Han.

455
00:31:58,400 --> 00:31:58,800
And then,

456
00:31:59,800 --> 00:32:00,640
she said you were

457
00:32:01,040 --> 00:32:03,560
impersonating him
and deceiving the public.

458
00:32:04,160 --> 00:32:05,720
She told everyone to get ready,

459
00:32:05,822 --> 00:32:07,240
and as soon as the new novel is live,

460
00:32:07,240 --> 00:32:09,022
they will launch attacks from all sides.

461
00:32:09,520 --> 00:32:10,200
She wants to...

462
00:32:11,120 --> 00:32:12,640
Make sure I never recover.

463
00:32:15,244 --> 00:32:16,720
That's pretty much what she meant.

464
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,640
What should we do, Mr. He Han?

465
00:32:20,200 --> 00:32:21,320
We all know

466
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:23,511
that you chose to step up
and pose as Phantom Knight

467
00:32:23,600 --> 00:32:25,920
just to lead the way
for us young authors.

468
00:32:26,440 --> 00:32:27,120
But we

469
00:32:27,200 --> 00:32:28,880
can't just watch the bullets hit you

470
00:32:28,880 --> 00:32:29,760
and not defend you.

471
00:32:30,444 --> 00:32:31,640
Didn't you say it yourself?

472
00:32:32,088 --> 00:32:33,880
Whoever holds
the banner for the dreamers

473
00:32:33,880 --> 00:32:35,320
is the Phantom Knight.

474
00:32:35,600 --> 00:32:36,000
Right?

475
00:32:37,560 --> 00:32:38,040
What?

476
00:32:58,755 --> 00:33:00,355
I'd like to ask you a few questions.

477
00:33:01,120 --> 00:33:01,560
Come on in.

478
00:33:08,120 --> 00:33:08,520
Sit.

479
00:33:14,440 --> 00:33:14,840
Go ahead.

480
00:33:14,911 --> 00:33:16,088
What do you want to ask?

481
00:33:26,400 --> 00:33:28,000
Regarding the Phantom Knight novel

482
00:33:28,111 --> 00:33:29,755
that Dingqi Platform
is about to release,

483
00:33:29,844 --> 00:33:31,133
you ghostwrote it, didn't you?

484
00:33:31,480 --> 00:33:32,120
I wrote it.

485
00:33:33,360 --> 00:33:34,640
Don't you look down on yourself?

486
00:33:36,320 --> 00:33:36,880
Why?

487
00:33:38,000 --> 00:33:39,040
The name "He Han"

488
00:33:39,133 --> 00:33:40,920
already has enough
weight in the industry,

489
00:33:41,377 --> 00:33:42,800
but you're still not satisfied.

490
00:33:43,800 --> 00:33:44,600
You want more.

491
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:46,840
You want to surpass yourself

492
00:33:47,320 --> 00:33:48,800
by standing at Phantom Knight's height

493
00:33:48,800 --> 00:33:50,440
to enjoy even more success.

494
00:33:51,440 --> 00:33:52,520
But have you ever thought

495
00:33:53,720 --> 00:33:55,200
that once all of this is exposed,

496
00:33:56,400 --> 00:33:57,880
the halo that the name "He Han"

497
00:33:57,880 --> 00:34:00,280
brought you
might disappear along with it?

498
00:34:04,177 --> 00:34:05,422
What are you laughing at?

499
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:07,440
Why does no one believe

500
00:34:07,440 --> 00:34:08,800
that I am the Phantom Knight?

501
00:34:13,960 --> 00:34:15,200
Have you ever heard the saying?

502
00:34:15,422 --> 00:34:16,680
The person you see in yourself

503
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:17,560
is not you.

504
00:34:18,244 --> 00:34:19,560
The person others see in you

505
00:34:19,960 --> 00:34:20,840
is not you, either.

506
00:34:21,640 --> 00:34:22,880
But the way you see others,

507
00:34:23,111 --> 00:34:24,080
that's who you are.

508
00:34:26,520 --> 00:34:28,360
The things you cherish as treasures

509
00:34:29,480 --> 00:34:31,200
might not even matter to anyone else.

510
00:34:32,480 --> 00:34:34,040
You make it sound so simple.

511
00:34:35,555 --> 00:34:37,933
Don't you want to return
to the top of the charts

512
00:34:38,622 --> 00:34:40,720
and to live in those
massive hotel suites again?

513
00:34:42,040 --> 00:34:43,200
I don't believe you at all.

514
00:34:44,955 --> 00:34:46,320
We're all just ordinary people.

515
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:49,280
Ordinary people say they don't care,

516
00:34:50,120 --> 00:34:51,240
but their actions are honest.

517
00:34:51,400 --> 00:34:52,080
I agree.

518
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:54,160
The action is honest.

519
00:34:54,800 --> 00:34:56,040
And mine is telling me

520
00:34:56,360 --> 00:34:57,720
that apartment was too big.

521
00:34:58,960 --> 00:35:00,920
One person doesn't need that much space.

522
00:35:01,680 --> 00:35:02,680
The extra space

523
00:35:02,866 --> 00:35:04,511
is just called emptiness.

524
00:35:08,422 --> 00:35:10,400
You might be No. 1
on the charts right now,

525
00:35:11,640 --> 00:35:13,160
but you have no one by your side

526
00:35:13,200 --> 00:35:15,600
to share that joy and achievement with.

527
00:35:18,280 --> 00:35:18,920
Is it worth it?

528
00:35:23,560 --> 00:35:24,600
Besides, you know

529
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:26,520
that this top spot

530
00:35:27,111 --> 00:35:28,760
is something you'll lose eventually.

531
00:35:33,760 --> 00:35:34,480
Be smart.

532
00:35:34,480 --> 00:35:36,822
An ordinary person should
understand what I'm saying.

533
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:38,800
You're saying

534
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:41,520
it's a case

535
00:35:42,600 --> 00:35:43,560
of sour grapes.

536
00:35:49,840 --> 00:35:50,640
I've tasted them.

537
00:35:51,711 --> 00:35:52,866
They weren't that good.

538
00:36:07,600 --> 00:36:08,320
How do I know

539
00:36:08,320 --> 00:36:10,577
you're not just finding
another excuse to tie me down?

540
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:14,600
Mr. Fan has already called you

541
00:36:14,800 --> 00:36:16,244
and explained the situation.

542
00:36:16,880 --> 00:36:17,880
Helping the company

543
00:36:18,280 --> 00:36:20,360
is helping me,
and it's helping yourself.

544
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:29,840
I know you're making other plans,

545
00:36:30,533 --> 00:36:32,577
but you haven't found
anything yet, right?

546
00:36:33,360 --> 00:36:34,240
For this current wave,

547
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:35,520
if we team up with Mr. Fan

548
00:36:35,800 --> 00:36:36,600
and Phantom Knight,

549
00:36:36,600 --> 00:36:38,133
we might not fully stage a comeback,

550
00:36:38,200 --> 00:36:40,266
but at least we can
get some breathing room.

